<GameData>
    <LocalizedText>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CIVILIZATION_BRAINROT_DSH_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Brainrot</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CIVILIZATION_BRAINROT_DSH_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>The Infinite FYP</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CIVILIZATION_BRAINROT_DSH_ADJECTIVE" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Brainrotted</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_TRIPLE_T_DSH_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Tung Tung Tung Sahur</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_BRAINROT_DSH_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Infinite Scrolling</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_BRAINROT_DSH_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Cities generate +20% [ICON_Culture] Culture but -10% [ICON_Science] Science. Gain [ICON_Culture] Culture whenever a city grows in [ICON_Citizen] Population.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_TRIPLE_T_DSH_BEAT_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Tung Tung Tung Sahur!</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_TRIPLE_T_DSH_BEAT_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>All units gain +1 Movement during the first 20 turns of an Era. Domestic [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes provide +2 [ICON_Food] Food to the starting city (to prepare for the fast).</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_SAHURINI_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Sahurini Arena</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_BUILDING_SAHURINI_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Brainrot unique building that replaces the Arena. Provides +3 [ICON_Amenities] Amenities and +2 [ICON_Culture] Culture. Boosts the [ICON_Pressure] Religious Pressure of this city by 100%.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LOADING_INFO_LEADER_DEFAULT" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Tung Tung Tung... SAHUR! Wake up, Great Leader, for the attention spans of your people are dwindling. Under your guidance, the Brainrot Empire will mog the world, taxing every Fanum and achieving the ultimate Skibidi victory. Let the beat of your drum wake the neighbors and the nations alike.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_PEDIA_LEADERS_PAGE_LEADER_TRIPLE_T_DSH_QUOTE" Language="en_US">
            <Text>"Tung tung tung... Sahur! If you aren't waking up to my beat, you're just getting negative rizz."</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_CIVINFO_BRAINROT_DSH_LOCATION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>The depths of the For You Page (FYP).</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CIVINFO_BRAINROT_DSH_SIZE" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Infinite scrolls of short-form content.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CIVINFO_BRAINROT_DSH_POPULATION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>100% Sigmas and Mewers.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CIVINFO_BRAINROT_DSH_CAPITAL" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Sahur, the city that never sleeps (because of the drumming).</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_AGENDA_TRIPLE_T_DSH_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>The Early Drummer</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_AGENDA_TRIPLE_T_DSH_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Likes civilizations with high [ICON_Food] Food. Dislikes those with low [ICON_Food] (He thinks they are starving their rizz).</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_KUDO_LEADER_TRIPLE_T_DSH_REASON_ANY" Language="en_US">
            <Text>(You have high Food yields)</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION_TRIPLE_T_DSH_S_RIZZ" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Triple T thinks you have massive rizz for having so much food.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_WARNING_LEADER_TRIPLE_T_DSH_REASON_ANY" Language="en_US">
            <Text>(You have low Food yields)</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION_TRIPLE_T_DSH_L_RIZZ" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Triple T thinks you have L rizz for your lack of food.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_CITIZEN_BRAINROT_DSH_MALE_1" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Skibidi</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CITIZEN_BRAINROT_DSH_MALE_2" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Baby Gronk</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CITIZEN_BRAINROT_DSH_FEMALE_1" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Livvy Dunne</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_CITIZEN_BRAINROT_DSH_FEMALE_2" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Ice Spice</Text>
        </Row>
    </LocalizedText>
</GameData>